<D>__{no.}
<C>__{the clerk of the house}
<D>__{mr. hutton? mr. william hutton, cast your vote.}
<A>__{hutton looks up from his prayer.}
<C>__{william hutton}
<D>__{william hutton, remembering at this moment his beloved brother, fredrick, votes against the amendment.}
